description.p:
Thus, the disclosed techniques provide one or more of the following advantages:





1) more accurate estimation of SOC of a battery in low diffusivity;

2) more accurate estimation of SOC of a battery at low temperature;

3) more accurate estimation of SOC of a battery with a large particle radius;

4) more accurate estimation of SOH of the battery; and

5) safer batteries by avoiding over-charge/over-discharge to avoid short circuits.
